h3-setting-customer-user-id-on-configura.translation:
### 在配置时设置 Customer User ID \{#setting-customer-user-id-on-configuration\}

如果在配置时已有用户 ID，只需将其作为 `customerUserId` 参数传递给 `.activate()` 方法：

```dart showLineNumbers title="Dart"
   try {
       await Adapty().activate(
           configuration: AdaptyConfiguration(apiKey: 'YOUR_API_KEY')
             ..withCustomerUserId(YOUR_CUSTOMER_USER_ID)
       );
   } catch (e) {
       // handle the error
   }
```

